Products
Our products are the starting point for many innovations that have made the world we occupy possible - as well as cleaner, safer and more comfortable.












You are hereHome » Overview 
Silica Sand Products Overview





Industrial Silica and Sand Proppants for Every Application
Silica sand, proppants and aplite minerals are the starting point for many innovations that have made the world of today possible - as well as cleaner, safer and more comfortable.
With over 250 unique products in our standard offerings, U.S. Silica is sure to have the perfect product with just the right grain size for your particular application. We provide silica sand and gravel for manufacturing, building, industrial and recreational use. Have a need that goes beyond what you see here? U.S. Silica’s Corporate Lab will help develop a custom blend or tailored product for your specific application.
Contact us today for information on standard or custom products and solutions.

 













