Why U.S. Silica
Supported by our history of excellence. Grounded in our practice of responsibility. Propelled by our spirit of innovation.












You are hereHome » Overview 
Why U.S. Silica?





What Makes U.S. Silica Different?
Supported by our history of excellence. Grounded in our practice of responsibility. Propelled by our spirit of innovation. You’ve helped make U.S. Silica a leader in industrial silica products and solutions by entrusting us with your businesses, resources and communities. Here’s what we’re doing – and what we’ll do tomorrow, and every day after that – to keep earning that trust: 
Advancing the science behind silica sand and other industrial minerals. Partnering with customers and industries to develop new products and serve new markets
Reinvesting in our facilities to maximize productivity and minimize costs, to provide top quality products at competitive costs
Employing good people, and providing them with the training and tools to be successful
Maintaining best in class safety performance
Acquiring high-quality reserves for sustained operations
Caring deeply for the communities in which we operate, and demonstrating it through environmental consciousness sustainable practices, quality jobs, and civic contributions
U.S. Silica Quality Policy
At U.S. Silica, we strive to be the industry leader in quality and service. We are committed to:
Exceeding our customers’ expectations
Continuously improving our performance
Increasing overall customer satisfaction
Our top-quality products, logistics solutions and customer service have set us apart from the competition for more than 100 years.  With our drive to adapt to new markets, new industry needs and new applications, we’re poised to grow even stronger in the future.
These may be the things that make us stand out from the competition – but they’re also the same things we’ve been practicing for a century. So in that regard, we haven’t changed. We’ve just continued to improve!

 













