Products
Our products are the starting point for many innovations that have made the world we occupy possible - as well as cleaner, safer and more comfortable.












You are hereHome » Ground Silica 
Ground Silica





Our SIL-CO-SIL® Ground Silica products are produced from high purity silica powder, precision ground from 45 to 250 micron topsize. Our ground silicas are inherently inert, bright white, with low moisture and are at least 99.5% Si02. SIL-CO-SIL’s properties improve coating hardness, chemical resistance, resin demand and dispersibility.
In comparison to other natural minerals, MIN-U-SIL® and SIL-CO-SIL offer the following benefits:
Improved Coating Hardness
Improved Chemical Resistance
Low Resin Demand
Comparable Color and Refractive Index
Consistent, moderate, near neutral pH
Dispersibility
Contact us today to order ground silica products
For Product Data Sheet Information Click Here

 













