Over a Century of QualityUS Silica's OTTAWA WHITE® and SHALE FRAC® proppants set the industry standard of quality and consistency for whole-grain α-quartz proppants.A Spirit of InnovationU.S. Silica is more than just a provider of industrial silica sand - we're an innovator in researching and developing performance-enhancing industrial silica products and solutions.With a Focus on SustainabilitySustainability is a core value at U.S. Silica, and the highest levels of our leadership embrace sustainability - not just through words, but also through actions.






The Premier Silica Sand Provider for Today and Tomorrow



U.S. Silica is a leading silica sand supplier with a focus on performance materials that are essential to modern living. Our state-of-the-art offerings are used in variety of Industries and Applications.
Oil and gas wells are more productive because our high-quality proppants improve flow rates and recovery from unconventional wells
Wind-powered and solar energy are more economical due to cost-effective manufacturing
Paints and coatings are more durable because of the quality of our crystal structure
Geothermal wells are more efficient due to improved heat transfer
Electronic devices are more scratch resistant because of the specially sized sand we offer
High-performance metal parts are more uniform because of our strict product and quality control
At U.S. Silica, our devotion to remaining on the cutting edge of technology helps improve the quality of every day - at home, at work and at play.

U.S. Silica'sSustainability Efforts
For more than 100 years, we have been committed to sustainable operations. Read more about U.S. Silica’s goals to ensure sustainability and review our annual Sustainability Reports here.

 
 





